Interface JavaClassModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.tinkerpop.frames.VertexFrame, WindupVertexFrame
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    AmbiguousJavaClassModel

    public interface JavaClassModel
extends WindupVertexFrame
    Represents a JavaClass, either from a .class file or a .java source file.
